        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to you regarding your published advert to recruit a person to look after your six-year-aged children. My eligibility for this post is explained below.",
        "My interaction with young people is trained in the developed world, and I relish children's companionship from my early childhood. Besides enjoyment, my experience dealing with teenagers came from an earlier experience as a teacher in the local primary school of my own country; consequently, my affection for kids forces me to apply for this opportunity.",
